author: jonl
msg: Fixed shared resource localization problem manifested in forminput example.
Image resources are now correctly shared under a URL that includes locale
and style (as originally intended).  Switching between locales will be correct
and efficient now.  The earlier code would result in unpredictable locale
shifts when used by multiple users.  It would also be very inefficient.
This checkin also includes a site update for Martijn to deploy with a fixes to introduction and features list per comments by various people.
